OVERVIEW
--------

1. Prepare Config/ENV files - everything 'include's these
2. Prepare an index file with packages, versions, build mode
3. Build with scripts/ifbuild, supply index file

NOTES
-----

- kernel 2.6 omits 'bash' dependency - uses 'wc', 'readlink', 'cut' (coreutils)


